1914年7月，一尊由雕塑家{{link-en|凱瑟琳·史考特|Kathleen Scott}}（海軍軍官[[羅伯特·史考特|羅伯特·史考特]]之妻）雕刻的史密斯船長紀念雕像，在[[利奇菲爾德|利奇菲爾德]]{{link-en|燈塔公園|Beacon Park}}博物館花園的西端揭幕<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.titanic-titanic.com/titanic_memorial-edward_john_smith.shtml |title=Smith information at |publisher=Titanic-titanic.com |date= |accessdate=2012-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100115171750/http://titanic-titanic.com/titanic_memorial-edward_john_smith.shtml |archive-date=2010-01-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，基座由康沃爾[[花崗岩|花崗岩]]製成，人像是青銅材質<ref name=noz>{{Citation | last =Noszlopy | first =George T.| authorlink = | title =Public Sculpture in Staffordshire & the Black Country|edition= | publisher = Liverpool University Press | year =2005 | location = | page = | isbn =978-0-85323-999-4  }}</ref>。由於史密斯是斯塔福德郡人，[[教區|教區]]中心為利奇菲爾德，所以選為紀念碑的所在地。這座雕像購過國家和當地公眾募款籌集資金，花費740[[英鎊|英鎊]]建造<ref name=LM>{{cite news |title=Captain of the Titanic is here to stay despite no local connection |author=|first=Andy |last=Kerr |newspaper=Lichfield Mercury |publisher= |location=Lichfield |isbn= |issn= |oclc= |pmid= |pmd= |bibcode= |doi= |id= |date=3 November 2011|page=29 }}</ref>。

