2010年，作為「人民公園」計劃的一部分，修復了這座雕像，耗資16,000英鎊清除青銅表面的綠銹<ref name="LM"/>。2011年，一場運動呼籲讓該雕像搬回史密斯的家鄉{{link-en|漢利 (斯塔福德郡)|Hanley, Staffordshire|漢利}}，但是沒有成功<ref name=pmslsa2>{{Citation| url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-stoke-staffordshire-14678152| title = Titanic Captain Smith statue Hanley move campaign| accessdate = 26 August 2011| publisher = BBC News| archive-date = 2018-10-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181005180837/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-stoke-staffordshire-14678152| dead-url = no}}</ref>。漢利市政廳舉行了紀念史密斯活動，上面有一塊牌匾<ref>{{cite book| last = Barczewski| first = Stephanie| year = 2006| title = ''Titanic'': A Night Remembered| url = https://archive.org/details/titanicnightreme0000barc|pages=[https://archive.org/details/titanicnightreme0000barc/page/172 172]–173| publisher = Continuum International Publishing Group| location = London| isbn = 978-1-85285-500-0}}</ref>：
